192
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:04,320
I immediately called my attorney, Douglas Reyes. Douglas was a veteran employment
and construction lawyer who had represented contractors in California for 30 years.

193
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:10,360
I sent him the entire file via an encrypted
link. Ten minutes later, Douglas called me back.

194
00:15:10,660 --> 00:15:16,320
Frank, this is not just a breach of contract.
Douglas said his voice grave. This is financial

195
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:21,760
fraud. The forgery of the lien waivers to obtain
public funds is a direct violation of California

196
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:27,760
Penal Code Section 1 on 15. But we have a problem.
Ryan and Brad know you have this data. They know

197
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:33,520
you kept copies. What do you mean? I ask. Douglas
sighed. I just received a notification on the

198
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:38,920
