200
00:15:44,260 --> 00:15:50,260
of Alameda. On what grounds? They are suing
you for theft of trade secrets, breach of your

201
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:54,940
non-disclosure agreement, and violation of
the Federal Computer Fraud and Abuse Act.

202
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:59,940
They claim that you illegally downloaded
proprietary corporate records and project

203
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:05,280
data before your termination. They are seeking an
